Additionally, it involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it deals with adversarial attacks and defense methods. It also falls under the sub-category of cryptography and security (cs.CR) as it aims to improve the robustness of models against attacks. Finally, it may also be related to neural networks (cs.NE) as it involves training deep neural networks.
